name: Growth = Death
description: We enter this world with little knowledge, a full soul and eager to absorb. We grow, we learn, our minds fill - while the soul empties to our 3D realities.   My final art exam - acrylic on canvas - digitised. Please contact me to purchase original artwork.  By Weslee Dee with love from Cape Town  Twitter  @KhoiSansVisage Instagram @wesleedee_theartist
